3. Data Flow
[ยื่นคำขอใหม่]
event-request-form.js
  → initPage()              fetch departments → populate dropdown
  → handleFileSelect()      validate size ≤ 10MB, store in attachFile
  → handleFileDrop()        drag & drop → store in attachFile
  → submitRequest()
      → validate            name + type + date required
      → autoGenerateRequestCode()
            query DB: REQ-YYYYMM-* → find maxSeq → REQ-YYYYMM-XXX
      → createRequest(payload)   POST /event_requests
      → uploadRequestFile()      POST storage/event-files/documents/
      → updateRequest()          PATCH attachment_url
      → redirect                 → event-requests-form.html

[หน้า List]
event-requests-form.js
  → loadData()
      → fetchRequests()     GET /event_requests?order=created_at.desc
      → fetchUsers()        GET /users
      → fetchDepts()        GET /departments
  → filterTable()           filter by search + status + type
  → renderTable()           สร้าง HTML rows
  → openReqPanel()          side panel แสดง detail + action buttons

[อนุมัติ]
event-requests-form.js
  → approveRequest(id)
      → createEventFromRequest()
            query DB: EVT-YYYYMM-* → find maxSeq → EVT-YYYYMM-XXX
            POST /events  (status: CONFIRMED)
      → updateRequest(id)   PATCH status=APPROVED, event_id=newEvent.id
      → reload

[ปฏิเสธ]
event-requests-form.js
  → openRejectModal(id)     เก็บ rejectTargetId
  → confirmReject()
      → validate            reason required
      → updateRequest(id)   PATCH status=REJECTED, reject_reason
      → reload
